ngstone.com/music/music-news/lil-durk-album-deep-thoughts-prison-1235298941/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rolling Stone</em></a> ).</p><p> If convicted, Banks could face life in federal prison.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-durk-to-release-new-album-deep-thoughts-from-prison-3847414">Lil Durk to release new album &#39;Deep Thoughts&#39; from prison</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
